<p>Dear {{ order_info.firstname }},</p>
<p>We are writing to update you on the status of your order with Order ID: <strong>{{ order_id }}</strong>.</p>

<p><strong>Current Order Status:</strong> {{ order_status }}</p>

<p>If your order has been shipped, you can expect it to arrive soon.</p>

<h3>Order Details:</h3>
<p><strong>Order Date:</strong> {{ date_added }}</p>
<p><strong>Shipping Address:</strong> {{ shipping_address }}</p>

<h3>Products Ordered:</h3>
<ul>
{% for product in products %}
    <li>{{ product.name }} x {{ product.quantity }} - {{ product.total }}</li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>

<p><strong>Total Amount:</strong> 
{% for total in totals %}
    {% if total.code == 'total' %}
        {{ total.text }}
    {% endif %}
{% endfor %}
</p>

<p><strong>Payment Method:</strong> {{ payment_method }}</p>

<p>If you have any questions, contact us at support@onlinesolutionsrx.com or call us at 123-456-7890.</p>

<p>Thank you for choosing OnlineSolutionsRx.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br/>The OnlineSolutionsRx Team</p>
